          What is the size of a website background image?
          1920 x 1080 pixels
          The best website background image size is 1920 x 1080 pixels, according to Malama Online Marketing, and the ideal ratio is 16:9. The dpi (dots per inch) should be at least 72, yet you still want to keep the file size as small as possible to minimize site load times.18 авг. 2018 г.

          How do I choose a background image for my website?
          In closing, remember these quick and easy tips to find the best background for your website: Choose images that are of high resolution (1024x768px minimum—if you have a bigger one, even better). Make sure those images are in landscape mode, and not in portrait mode. Only tile images that are meant to be tiled.
